column10: I was NB on a bikeshare bike on the trail along US-50, crossing Pershing Dr. in the Xwalk w/ "walk" signal. Driver in a Lexus (I think) SUV EB on Pershing Dr, approaching red light, entered left lane then stopped late, nearly hit me in Xwalk
Large Truck turning right across bike lane almost crushed me.
